<header class="comment-header">
<p class="comment-author" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
<span itemprop="name">Asha P</span> <span class="says">says</span> </p>
<p class="comment-meta"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2017-06-15T14:51:24+00:00" itemprop="datePublished"><a href="https://cookieandkate.com/2017/how-to-make-basil-pesto/#comment-454505" class="comment-time-link" itemprop="url">June 15, 2017 at 2:51 PM</a></time></p> </header>
<div class="comment-content" itemprop="text">
<p>I always blanch my basil leaves for 15-20 seconds in hot water followed by a dunk in ice water before making pesto. This method will maintain a vivid green pesto for a week or so in the refrigerator</p>
</div>
